org.eclipse.graphiti.mm.algorithms

Interface Image

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AbstractStyle, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, GraphicsAlgorithm, GraphicsAlgorithmContainer, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, PropertyContainer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ImageImpl

    public interface Image
extends GraphicsAlgorithm
    A representation of the model object 'Image'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Id
    • Stretch H
    • Stretch V
    • Proportional

    See Also:
    AlgorithmsPackage.getImage()
